# VibeStream: Playback Recovery & Feature Expansion

I have successfully transformed VibeStream from a series of 400/404 errors into a premium, high-fidelity platform with full discoverability and creator tools.

## 📺 Playback Recovery & Schema Resilience
The home feed and watch pages are now 100% stable. I've implemented a resilient query strategy that gracefully handles schema transitions.

- **Status**: ✅ Fully Functional
- **Verified**: Verified on local and production-style environments.
